dialogue.dialogue: The way this betch thinks she can manifest a brownstone when her sourdough starter’s in hospice.
Blind child dreams of grand estates, yet has not tended to the hearth she already possesses.
For real. Babe — you can’t feng shui your way into a mortgage if you’ve got laundry chair energy.
Indeed. The Empress tends her domain with reverence. Every kingdom begins with a single, well-loved room.
Totes. The Etsy Queen crafts that shit. Her dynasty’s built one thrifted frame and clearance-rack candle at a time.
Honor your dwelling, however modest, and the palace will reveal itself in due time.
So yeah — big house energy starts with big vibe energy. Light a candle, fold the throw blanket, and act like Zillow’s watching.
